long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Prefix searches in the address bar with 'v8' and get suggestions from the V8 API docs.

Choose from several V8 API versions.

Suggestions are generated locally from API data; no keystrokes are sent over the network, nor any special permissions needed.
